\setlegalmoves{h8}{pawn}
\end{chessboard}

\end{document}
```

This code will generate a chessboard with all the pieces placed on the board according to the FEN notation. You can customize the position of the pieces by modifying the `setlegalmoves` commands inside the `chessboard` environment.

Note that the `chessboard` package is not part of the standard LaTeX distribution, so you might need to install it separately. You can find more information about the package and how to install it in the package documentation: [chessboard package](https://ctan.org/pkg/chessboard)

